stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING_EMAIL : Inscription
    PENDING_EMAIL --> PENDING_APPROVAL : confirm-email
    PENDING_APPROVAL --> ACTIVE : admin approve + provisioning
    PENDING_APPROVAL --> REJECTED : admin reject
    ACTIVE --> [*]

    note right of PENDING_APPROVAL
        Auto-provision si
        KSM_KERNEL_AUTO_PROVISION_ARTISTS=true
    end note
